de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor

Class AbstractHeartRateSensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor.Sensor<HeartRateGattLibrary>
      • de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor.AbstractHeartRateSensor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HeartRateSensor, SensorCommands
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdidasMiCoachHRM, PolarH7, TomTomHRM

    public abstract class AbstractHeartRateSensor
extends Sensor<HeartRateGattLibrary>
implements HeartRateSensor
    Abstraction for heart rate sensors, which are using the GATT characteristics (0x2A37). Every new heart rate sensor, which is compliant with the Bluetooth specification, may inherit from this class.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
    See Also:
    Heart Rate Measurement
